.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
creates a Janet bundle in the current directory.
At minimum,
a directory called
.Ar name
that contains an
.Sy info file
will be created.
.Pp
By default,
.Nm
will prompt the user for certain information that was not included
in the command-line invocation.
See
.Fl "-no-ask"
below for more details.
.
